title: Seawolves Beat UNH, Fall to St. Joe's in Fall Championship (SMCC Athletics)
text: ( Source : SMCC Athletics ) Concord, NH - At today's YSCC fall tournament the Seawolves downed the Wildcats of UNH , 3-1, in the first round but fell to the College of St. Joe's (VT) in the championship game, 4-1. Seawolves' pitcher Nate Boyle
